---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Guide">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner docs">
      <p class="eyebrow">Guide</p>
      <h1>Arena guide</h1>
      <p class="lead">Everything you need to start collecting, battling, and earning in Cheems Arena.</p>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Getting started</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Create a Solana-compatible wallet and secure your seed phrase.</li>
          <li>Connect your wallet to the Cheems Arena marketplace.</li>
          <li>Buy your first Cheemy pack and start building your deck.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Card rarities</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Common cards form the backbone of every deck.</li>
          <li>Rare cards introduce unique mechanics and stronger stats.</li>
          <li>Epic cards carry lore and abilities that define playstyles.</li>
          <li>Legendary cards are the scarcest and most powerful in the Cheemsrealm.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Battle mechanics</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Build a deck of 20 cards using any combination of elements and rarities.</li>
          <li>Challenge opponents in ranked or casual matches.</li>
          <li>Use element synergies and card abilities to outplay your rival.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Trading safely</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Verify NFT authenticity on Solana explorers before trading.</li>
          <li>Use only official marketplace links to avoid scams.</li>
          <li>Never share your wallet seed phrase with anyone.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 22px;
    color: #354052;
  }

  pre {
    overflow: auto;
    margin: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #111827;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 18px;
  }
</style>
